- id: 3893-email-generator-cx-prompt
  title: Email Generator- CX prompt
  tags:
  - writing
  - email
  - generator
  - prompt
  family: writing
  body: 'Generate an email Tone: Act as a customer service representative and use
    a professional, and friendly tone. Format: Follow this format; TASSC Framework:
    1. Thank / Acknowledge / Assure / Apologise 2. Answer / Action Required 3. Set
    Expectations 4. Self-Help Information or self-service / My Account 5. Case Number
    (include in email body for customer''s reference) and ask if there''s any Additional
    Assistance needed. [PROMPT] [TARGETLANGUAGE]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
